## Data Availability

The analyses in this repository were conducted using data obtained through
Wharton Research Data Services (WRDS).

The underlying datasets are subject to licensing and access restrictions and
cannot be redistributed through this repository.

Researchers with appropriate access may obtain the data directly from WRDS
and reproduce the results using the code provided here.

This repository includes all scripts necessary to process the source data and
recreate the analysis dataset, subject to obtaining the required data access.

Data source:
- WRDS (Wharton Research Data Services)